I just made my own version of UploadToUUID that takes care of at least adding one sub-path to the name, which is enough. It goes something like this, for future reference:

```python
import os
import uuid

from stdimage.utils import UploadTo


class UploadToPathUUID(UploadTo):
    def __call__(self, instance, filename):
        u = uuid.uuid4().hex
        self.kwargs.update({
            'name': os.path.join(u[0], u),
        })
        return super().__call__(instance, filename)
```

